dict.acceptation: （在）海外的，（在）国外的；（向或来自）外国的；

sent.orig: Responsible for purchasing orders from overseas suppliers. Keep good relationship with overseas suppliers arrangement on logistic.
sent.trans: 负责向海外供应商发送订单，和海外供应商保持良好的合作关系。

sent.orig: Is there any withholding tax liability for the expenses paid to overseas company overseas quality inspection?
sent.trans: 我单位委托境外企业实施商品检测的费用，是否需要代扣代缴预提所得税？

sent.orig: Many overseas Chinese living abroad, is a famous hometown of overseas Chinese.
sent.trans: 旅居海外华侨众多，是个著名侨乡。

sent.orig: Willing to travel overseas for training; Previous related overseas training experience will be an advantage.
sent.trans: 愿意出国培训；有相关海外培训经历者优先。

sent.orig: For this purpose, the benefit of overseas experience and assistance of overseas expertise would be useful.
sent.trans: 在这方面，海外经验和外国的专业知识可供借鉴。
